headline: ValuEngine Weekly Market Summary And Commentary
summary: Markets ended the week ending Aug. 29 mixed, with sector ETFs stable but notable strength in Energy, Financials, and Small Caps. Reg. stocks, tech and select growth names saw outsized gains.
